# Export Engine Rules

## Permitted Paths (Write Access)
- `src/engine/codegen/**` — all code generator scripts
- `src/engine/templates/**` — Handlebars templates
- `src/engine/validator.js`
- `src/data/devices.json`
- `src/data/animationPresets.json`
- `src/utils/lvglColor.js`
- `src/utils/lvglCoord.js`
- `src/utils/fontUtils.js`

## Restricted Paths (Read-Only)
- All files in `src/pages/**`
- All files in `src/components/**`
- All files in `src/store/**`

## Engine Specific Rules
- Functions in codegen must accept plain configuration objects (do not pass React state variables directly).
- Generates C code outputs as raw strings.
- Support LVGL v8.x API constructs (do not use v9.x functions).
- Coordinate positioning: use `lv_obj_set_pos(obj, x, y)` for absolute layout styling.
- Colors: format outputs using `lv_color_hex(0xRRGGBB)`.
- Default fonts: map standard LVGL fonts to Montserrat variables (e.g. `&lv_font_montserrat_16`).
- Define DISPLAY_ROTATION and swap macros in display_driver.h to allow IDE-level configuration of screens.
- Pin conflict validation must run before project compression.
